code: @Override public void readFrom(StreamInput in) throws IOException {     super.readFrom(in).     clusterName = new ClusterName(in).     node = in.readOptionalWriteable(DiscoveryNode::new). }
@Override public void writeTo(StreamOutput out) throws IOException {     super.writeTo(out).     clusterName.writeTo(out).     out.writeOptionalWriteable(node). }
